AMCOL International, headquartered in Hoffman Estates, IL, produces and markets a wide range of specialty mineral products used for industrial, environmental and consumer-related applications.  AMCOL is the parent of American Colloid Company, CETCO (Colloid Environmental Technologies Company), CETCO Oilfield Services Company and the transportation operations, Ameri-co Carriers, Inc. and Ameri-co Logistics, Inc.  AMCOLs common stock is traded on the New York Stock Exchange under the symbol ACO.  AMCOLs web address is
