That press release dated, April 27, 2012 and titled AMCOL INTERNATIONAL CORPORATION (NYSE:ACO) REPORTS FIRST QUARTER RESULTS is attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1.
ITEM 9.01                      Financial Statements and Exhibits
(d)           The following exhibit is furnished with this document:
                  
